self.name: Update
self.descriptionExcerpt: Object contains info on events occured.

nodes.name: updateNewMessage
nodes.description: New message in a private chat or in a legacy group.

nodes.name: updateMessageID
nodes.description: Sent message with random_id client identifier was assigned an identifier.

nodes.name: updateDeleteMessages
nodes.description: Messages were deleted.

nodes.name: updateUserTyping
nodes.description: The user is preparing a message; typing, recording, uploading, etc. This update is valid for 6 seconds. If no repeated update received after 6 seconds, it should be considered that the user stopped doing whatever he's been doing.

nodes.name: updateChatUserTyping
nodes.description: The user is preparing a message in a group; typing, recording, uploading, etc. This update is valid for 6 seconds. If no repeated update received after 6 seconds, it should be considered that the user stopped doing whatever he's been doing.

nodes.name: updateChatParticipants
nodes.description: Composition of chat participants changed.

nodes.name: updateUserStatus
nodes.description: Contact status update.

nodes.name: updateUserName
nodes.description: Changes the user's first name, last name and username.

nodes.name: updateUserPhoto
nodes.description: Change of contact's profile photo.

nodes.name: updateNewEncryptedMessage
nodes.description: New encrypted message.

nodes.name: updateEncryptedChatTyping
nodes.description: Interlocutor is typing a message in an encrypted chat. Update period is 6 second. If upon this time there is no repeated update, it shall be considered that the interlocutor stopped typing.

nodes.name: updateEncryption
nodes.description: Change of state in an encrypted chat.

nodes.name: updateEncryptedMessagesRead
nodes.description: Communication history in an encrypted chat was marked as read.

nodes.name: updateChatParticipantAdd
nodes.description: New group member.

nodes.name: updateChatParticipantDelete

There are new updates in the specified channel, the client must fetch them.
If the difference is too long or if the channel isn't currently in the states, start fetching from the specified pts.
